    dctm:description """The StreamForge Catalog Assistant is a synthetic AI agent included to support examples of RAG over the StreamForge data catalog. It is used to explain how text-heavy documentation chunks and graph-heavy lineage facts can be surfaced to a language model through embedding generation.

