    dp:embedding_note """Search Relevance Experiment Report Q4 2025 Chunk 03 is an instance of Document Chunk.
Search Relevance Experiment Report Q4 2025 Chunk 03 is an instance of Catalog Asset."""@en .

sf:Search_Relevance_Experiment_Report_Q4_2025_Chunk_04 a owl:NamedIndividual,
        prov:Entity,
        docs:Document_Chunk,
        dp:Catalog_Asset ;
    rdfs:label "Search Relevance Experiment Report Q4 2025 Chunk 04"@en ;
    docs:chunk_index 4 ;
    docs:chunk_text "We ran a two-week A/B test on 10% of logged-in traffic. Treatment adjusted the weighting of freshness and creator authority signals for ambiguous queries."@en ;
    docs:chunk_title "Experiment design"@en ;
    docs:is_chunk_of sf:Search_Relevance_Experiment_Report_Q4_2025 ;
    dp:embedding_note """Search Relevance Experiment Report Q4 2025 Chunk 04 is an instance of Document Chunk.
Search Relevance Experiment Report Q4 2025 Chunk 04 is an instance of Catalog Asset."""@en .

sf:Search_Relevance_Experiment_Report_Q4_2025_Chunk_05 a owl:NamedIndividual,
        prov:Entity,
        docs:Document_Chunk,
        dp:Catalog_Asset ;
    rdfs:label "Search Relevance Experiment Report Q4 2025 Chunk 05"@en ;
    docs:chunk_index 5 ;
    docs:chunk_text "Treatment reduced query reformulation by 4.2% relative and improved successful clicks by 1.8% relative. Gains were largest for navigation queries and trending topics."@en ;
    docs:chunk_title "Findings"@en ;
    docs:is_chunk_of sf:Search_Relevance_Experiment_Report_Q4_2025 ;
    dp:embedding_note """Search Relevance Experiment Report Q4 2025 Chunk 05 is an instance of Document Chunk.
Search Relevance Experiment Report Q4 2025 Chunk 05 is an instance of Catalog Asset."""@en .

sf:Search_Relevance_Experiment_Report_Q4_2025_Chunk_06 a owl:NamedIndividual,
        prov:Entity,
        docs:Document_Chunk,
        dp:Catalog_Asset ;
    rdfs:label "Search Relevance Experiment Report Q4 2025 Chunk 06"@en ;
    docs:chunk_index 6 ;
    docs:chunk_text "Promote the treatment model to 50% traffic and monitor regressions in rare-query performance. For governance, publish a stable 'search_experiments' view so metrics are reproducible across teams."@en ;
    docs:chunk_title "Recommendations"@en ;
    docs:is_chunk_of sf:Search_Relevance_Experiment_Report_Q4_2025 ;
    dp:embedding_note """Search Relevance Experiment Report Q4 2025 Chunk 06 is an instance of Document Chunk.
Search Relevance Experiment Report Q4 2025 Chunk 06 is an instance of Catalog Asset."""@en .

sf:Trust_And_Safety_Moderation_Audit_Summary_2025_Chunk_01 a owl:NamedIndividual,
        prov:Entity,
        docs:Document_Chunk,
        dp:Catalog_Asset ;
    rdfs:label "Trust And Safety Moderation Audit Summary 2025 Chunk 01"@en ;
    docs:chunk_index 1 ;
    docs:chunk_text "This audit summarizes moderation actions and evaluates whether policy enforcement is consistent, timely, and auditable. It focuses on takedowns and reinstatements."@en ;
    docs:chunk_title "Purpose"@en ;
    docs:is_chunk_of sf:Trust_And_Safety_Moderation_Audit_Summary_2025 ;
    dp:embedding_note """Trust And Safety Moderation Audit Summary 2025 Chunk 01 is an instance of Document Chunk.
Trust And Safety Moderation Audit Summary 2025 Chunk 01 is an instance of Catalog Asset."""@en .

sf:Trust_And_Safety_Moderation_Audit_Summary_2025_Chunk_02 a owl:NamedIndividual,
        prov:Entity,
        docs:Document_Chunk,
        dp:Catalog_Asset ;
    rdfs:label "Trust And Safety Moderation Audit Summary 2025 Chunk 02"@en ;
    docs:chunk_index 2 ;
    docs:chunk_text "We used the Moderation Actions data product (event-level) and joined to the Video Metadata data product for canonical content attributes such as category and privacy state."@en ;
    docs:chunk_title "Data products used"@en ;
    docs:is_chunk_of sf:Trust_And_Safety_Moderation_Audit_Summary_2025 ;
    dp:embedding_note """Trust And Safety Moderation Audit Summary 2025 Chunk 02 is an instance of Document Chunk.
Trust And Safety Moderation Audit Summary 2025 Chunk 02 is an instance of Catalog Asset."""@en .

sf:Trust_And_Safety_Moderation_Audit_Summary_2025_Chunk_03 a owl:NamedIndividual,
        prov:Entity,
        docs:Document_Chunk,
        dp:Catalog_Asset ;
    rdfs:label "Trust And Safety Moderation Audit Summary 2025 Chunk 03"@en ;
    docs:chunk_index 3 ;
    docs:chunk_text "Median time from flag to decision improved from 18 hours to 11 hours. However, a long tail of cases exceeded 7 days, often due to missing metadata needed for review."@en ;
    docs:chunk_title "Findings on timeliness"@en ;
    docs:is_chunk_of sf:Trust_And_Safety_Moderation_Audit_Summary_2025 ;
    dp:embedding_note """Trust And Safety Moderation Audit Summary 2025 Chunk 03 is an instance of Document Chunk.
Trust And Safety Moderation Audit Summary 2025 Chunk 03 is an instance of Catalog Asset."""@en .

sf:Trust_And_Safety_Moderation_Audit_Summary_2025_Chunk_04 a owl:NamedIndividual,
        prov:Entity,
        docs:Document_Chunk,
        dp:Catalog_Asset ;
    rdfs:label "Trust And Safety Moderation Audit Summary 2025 Chunk 04"@en ;
    docs:chunk_index 4 ;
    docs:chunk_text "Some actions were missing reviewer identifiers, making post-hoc audits difficult. We recommend enforcing required fields at ingestion and generating operational alerts when fields are null."@en ;
    docs:chunk_title "Auditability gaps"@en ;
    docs:is_chunk_of sf:Trust_And_Safety_Moderation_Audit_Summary_2025 ;
    dp:embedding_note """Trust And Safety Moderation Audit Summary 2025 Chunk 04 is an instance of Document Chunk.
Trust And Safety Moderation Audit Summary 2025 Chunk 04 is an instance of Catalog Asset."""@en .

sf:Trust_And_Safety_Moderation_Audit_Summary_2025_Chunk_05 a owl:NamedIndividual,
        prov:Entity,
        docs:Document_Chunk,
        dp:Catalog_Asset ;
    rdfs:label "Trust And Safety Moderation Audit Summary 2025 Chunk 05"@en ;
    docs:chunk_index 5 ;
    docs:chunk_text "Add lineage records linking moderation events to the policy version used at decision time. Maintain a documented retention policy for moderation logs and related evidence."@en ;
    docs:chunk_title "Recommended controls"@en ;
    docs:is_chunk_of sf:Trust_And_Safety_Moderation_Audit_Summary_2025 ;
    dp:embedding_note """Trust And Safety Moderation Audit Summary 2025 Chunk 05 is an instance of Document Chunk.
Trust And Safety Moderation Audit Summary 2025 Chunk 05 is an instance of Catalog Asset."""@en .

sf:Trust_And_Safety_Moderation_Audit_Summary_2025_Chunk_06 a owl:NamedIndividual,
        prov:Entity,
        docs:Document_Chunk,
        dp:Catalog_Asset ;
    rdfs:label "Trust And Safety Moderation Audit Summary 2025 Chunk 06"@en ;
    docs:chunk_index 6 ;
    docs:chunk_text "Publish a canonical moderation audit view and provide a standard dashboard for compliance stakeholders. Track policy drift via quarterly sampling and review."@en ;
    docs:chunk_title "Next steps"@en ;
    docs:is_chunk_of sf:Trust_And_Safety_Moderation_Audit_Summary_2025 ;
    dp:embedding_note """Trust And Safety Moderation Audit Summary 2025 Chunk 06 is an instance of Document Chunk.
Trust And Safety Moderation Audit Summary 2025 Chunk 06 is an instance of Catalog Asset."""@en .

