prov:Activity a owl:Class ;
    rdfs:label "Activity"@en ;
    dctm:description "In PROV-O, an Activity represents an occurrence (a process, action, or event-like happening) that takes place over time and may use entities and/or generate entities. Activities are typically linked to Agents via properties such as prov:wasAssociatedWith, and to Entities via prov:used and prov:wasGeneratedBy."@en ;
    dctm:source <https://www.w3.org/TR/prov-o/> ;
    rdfs:comment "Use prov:Activity to represent processes or actions that happen over time and that interact with entities, often with accountable agents."@en ;
    rdfs:isDefinedBy prov: ;
    rdfs:subClassOf owl:Thing,
        prov:Activity ;
    owl:equivalentClass prov:Activity ;
    skos:definition "An activity is something that occurs over a period of time and acts upon or with entities; it may include consuming, processing, transforming, modifying, relocating, using, or generating entities."@en ;
    skos:editorialNote "If your system distinguishes 'event' vs 'process', you can subclass prov:Activity accordingly; PROV itself stays intentionally general."@en ;
    skos:example "enenenenenenenenen@prefix rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>",
        "Example: :Load_CSV_Run_2026_01_15 a prov:Activity ; prov:used :Input_CSV_File ; prov:generated :Staged_RDF_Graph ; prov:wasAssociatedWith :ETL_Service_Account ."@en ;
    skos:note "enenenenenenenenen@prefix rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>",
        "An activity is something that occurs over a period of time and acts upon or with entities; it may include consuming, processing, transforming, modifying, relocating, using, or generating entities."@en,
        "Example: :Load_CSV_Run_2026_01_15 a prov:Activity ; prov:used :Input_CSV_File ; prov:generated :Staged_RDF_Graph ; prov:wasAssociatedWith :ETL_Service_Account ."@en,
        "If your system distinguishes 'event' vs 'process', you can subclass prov:Activity accordingly; PROV itself stays intentionally general."@en ;
    dp:embedding_note """Activity is a kind of Activity.
Data Analysis Activity is a kind of Activity.
Domain Concept Change is a kind of Activity.
Kafka Activity is a kind of Activity.
Video Playback is a kind of Activity.
owl:Nothing is a kind of Activity.
Kafka Publish Activity is a kind of Activity.
Kafka Consume Activity is a kind of Activity.
Kafka Replay Activity is a kind of Activity.
Activity has description In PROV-O, an Activity represents an occurrence (a process, action, or event-like happening) that takes place over time and may use entities and/or generate entities. Activities are typically linked to Agents via properties such as prov:wasAssociatedWith, and to Entities via prov:used and prov:wasGeneratedBy.
Activity has source https://www.w3.org/TR/prov-o/.
Activity has comment Use prov:Activity to represent processes or actions that happen over time and that interact with entities, often with accountable agents.
Activity is defined by http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#.
